title: Hyper-V Checkpoints
agents: windows
catalog: os/windows
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 For a virtual machine running on Hyper-V this check reports the number of
 checkpoints and the age if oldest and latest checkpoint. 

 In order to run, its needed to copy the hyperv_host.ps1 script to the plugin
 folder. The plugin sends data for all virutal machines as piggyback data in the
 agent output of the Hyper-V host.

item:
 None

inventory:
 On each VM one check is generated if there is checkpoint information available.

